[0945] formula_1 | Q: How much faster in percentage is the champion than the driver who finished the race last in the 2008 Australian Grand Prix?
       Tables: [lapTimes, qualifying, drivers, circuits, status, constructors, driverStandings, constructorResults, races, results, seasons, constructorStandings, pitStops] | Iters: 16 | Time: 126.9s | ✅
